{"tid":522530,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金正恩委員長今日34歲生日啦，大家有咩祝福想同金仔講","createTime":"2018-01-07T16:02:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T06:16:06.000Z","uid":92376,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4e48358fd7495a05443b1b038226f3ea05adb2be","tid":522530,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T16:02:32.000Z","msg":"又大一歲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望金仔繼續撚化侵侵，誓不低頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4483ae0a23b8d266c4ef45b5fd44baf753353ca","tid":522530,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T03:41:08.000Z","msg":"北韓最高領導人金正恩，今天過34歲生日，北韓媒體靜悄悄，沒有報導有關他慶生活動的消息。 <br />\n<br />\n據韓聯社今天報導，截至今天上午，北韓媒體沒有提及金正恩生日相關內容，也沒有報導金正恩慶生相關活動以及居民放假消息。這與北韓把金正恩祖父、已故北韓領導人金日成生日4月15日和金正恩父親金正日生日2月16日，分別指定為「太陽節」和「光明星節」，並舉辦盛大的慶生活動，形成鮮明對照。 <br />\n<br />\n據有關方面分析，雖然金正恩掌權已過六個年頭，但北韓尚未把金正恩生日指定為紀念日，可能是因為對外公開金正恩的出生時期，將方才年過而立的年紀人，捧為偉大領袖，多少有些尷尬。<br />\n<br />\n低調，愛民如子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36ba7267adc20c7ab8c456ca46ae2079acb7924b","tid":522530,"uid":139815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T03:53:15.000Z","msg":"正恩OPPA<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">사랑해</span></span>"},{"pid":"69665a812417f72aba3b69b6592b67af39fbef30","tid":522530,"uid":52459,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T03:55:14.000Z","msg":"佢高傲，但係宅心仁厚，佢低調，但係受萬民敬仰。佢可以將神賜比人類嘅核彈運用得出神入化，佢可以射出堪稱火之藝術嘅超級導彈，佢究竟係神仙嘅化身？定係地獄嚟嘅使者？無人知道。但係可以肯定，每一個人都畀佢一個稱號──火箭人。"},{"pid":"8021d88c2a4f540ab204e3b6ff2e6b2a06fb8463","tid":522530,"uid":139993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T03:58:12.000Z","msg":"希望金仔用實際行動話比侵侵聽：「我粒制堅係work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」"},{"pid":"a5c7fd1f7b720f1a818e7f3ba36aebee47a25946","tid":522530,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:02:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9a879464f63b0021cb0a71aeac55822a961b645","tid":522530,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:28:51.000Z","msg":"中共唔係fd子黎架，拎完佢d錢就算喇"},{"pid":"6319074e4fa6ff3c586652af5f8a69cb94cf6446","tid":522530,"uid":127123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"祝早日統一韓國,之後再打日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"599a2e37b0e7cc0b788031311c152e0c1ad4f594","tid":522530,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:38:14.000Z","msg":"金仔加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dff41ac77e0d00c73388bfe877a6b5c50e47f08c","tid":522530,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:44:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d35d97722cf45f928726dc8710c59cf446dd0dfe","tid":522530,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:46:24.000Z","msg":"北韓人民祝願白頭山既希望繼續帶領住佢地捍衛民族尊嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11d3cded7c3fe793a803414d1b24144b89b3c38","tid":522530,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T04:49:27.000Z","msg":"祝你一世射唔出"},{"pid":"51964183a043b4edd528fbcc3b0956c27c3841e7","tid":522530,"uid":40550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T06:16:06.000Z","msg":"夠薑你就㩒制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}